<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Oct1934"><font color="red">16 October 1934</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Giorgio Joyce): Thanks for your wire on the 8th. We and Jolas drove to Rapperswil for tea and then round the lake &hellip; A 30-year wedding should be called a &lsquo;findrinny one&rsquo;. Findrinny is a kind of white gold mixed with silver </div>
